// ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ Region mapping ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
function getRegion(zip) {
  const prefix = parseInt(zip?.substring(0, 3) || "0");
  if (prefix >= 900 && prefix <= 908) return "Los Angeles";
  if (prefix >= 910 && prefix <= 918) return "Inland Empire / San Bernardino";
  if (prefix >= 919 && prefix <= 921) return "San Diego";
  if (prefix >= 922 && prefix <= 928) return "Central / Desert";
  if (prefix >= 930 && prefix <= 935) return "Central Coast";
  if (prefix >= 936 && prefix <= 939) return "Central Valley South";
  if (prefix >= 940 && prefix <= 949) return "Bay Area";
  if (prefix >= 950 && prefix <= 953) return "South Bay / Santa Cruz";
  if (prefix >= 954 && prefix <= 956) return "Central Valley North";
  if (prefix >= 957 && prefix <= 959) return "Sacramento / Gold Country";
  if (prefix >= 960 && prefix <= 961) return "Northern California";
  if (prefix >= 962 && prefix <= 966) return "Military / Other";
  if (prefix === 909) return "LA Adjacent";
  return "Other";
}

